            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Cradle of Civilization</h3>Observing the humanity distribution, constructions around the planet, the geography and the relationship between people, we observe the idea that an unique cradle of civilization is not consistent with our current knowledge. Although the origin of specie in Africa is widely accepted, the hipotesis of all civilization arises from Mesopotamia looks like improbable. With this context, we present in the map of this sectiion, this six cradle of civilizations teach in <i>History Tracers</i>",
